profile:
Award Winning Specialists!
416-236-8721

A&A Masonry is an award-winning Toronto based firm specializing in almost everything exterior.  Specialties include Stone work, Interlock, Interlocking, Paver stones, paving stones, Natural Stone, Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Masonry, brick repair, brick restoration, tuck pointing, waterproofing, foundation repairs, concrete steps, porches, walkways, caulking services (windows & doors), chimney repair and general exterior restorations for residential, commercial and industrial customers.

A&A is dedicated to providing the highest quality on every job. With a proud team of qualified artisans, we strive to complete every project in a timely and safe manner.

Our mission is to offer a unique and reliable service in anything Exterior within the Greater Toronto Area, differentiating ourselves from the competition by means of always delivering what we promise, on time and on budget.

Our commitment to excellence is our core value.
Customer satisfaction is our main goal, and we reach it every day by relying on our attention to customer service. By providing customized solutions for every job, we guarantee that we will never compromise on quality, safety and efficiency.

This approach together with our experience and knowledge allows us to effectively handle a wide variety of projects, from small to big, indoors or outdoors, renovations or repairs. 

We service:  Toronto, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Thornhill, Richmond Hill, York, North York, East York, Mimico, Hamilton, Brampton, Bolton and surrounding areas. 

For FREE ESTIMATE CALL: 416-236-8721

Being Masonry Contractors, Concrete Contractors, Stone  Contractors & Waterproofing Contractors we specialize in:
Stone work, Interlocking Natural Stone & Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Tuck Pointing, Chimney Repair, Chimney Rebuild, Chimney Restoration, tuckpointing, Brickwork, Brick Repair, Brick Replacement, Parging, Waterproofing, Foundation Repair, Concrete Resurfacing, Concrete Porches, Concrete Steps, Patios and Walkways, Flagstone, Cultured Stone, Caulking services (windows and doors), Masonry, Masonry repair, steps, concrete porches, concrete walkways and patios, caulking services.

Green Side Up Contracting Inc. is a professional member of Landscape Ontario & we are an authorized TrexPro - Platinum status!

Over the last 22 years, we have established ourselves within the construction industry as an honest and reputable contractor.  We have earned this reputation by shaping the company around four core values: honesty, transparency, quality of workmanship, backed by above industry-standard warranties!

As the President of Green Side Up Contracting Inc. and a board member of the Toronto Chapter of Landscape Ontario, PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT and delivering EXCELLENCE are two of Jay's key priorities.

         ****************************10 YEAR STRUCTURAL WARRANTY - FENCING ****************************

Green Side Up Contracting Inc is a consistent award-winning, construction company that focuses on delivering high-quality workmanship and superior customer service.  We put our trust into our clients with extremely favorable payment terms - pay when the job is completed! We are active members of our community and believe in helping those who are less fortunate.

Services provided include but are not limited to:

-> Fence Construction (80' linear feet minumum)
 
-> Interlocking & Landscape Construction

-> Deck Construction (200 sq foot minumim) 

    - Trex
    - Cedar

***

Not only does Green Side Up Contracting Inc focus on PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT by offering a TEN-YEAR structural WARRANTY on fencing, we also believe that doing business together should be simple and transparent.

***

Please use our SELF SERVE CALCULATORS to obtain an INSTANT ESTIMATE for your DECK, FENCE or INTERLOCK project:

FENCE CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/fence-building-calculator/

DECK CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/deck-calculator/

INTERLOCKING CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/interlock-cost-calculator/

***

Please be sure to check our work by visiting:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/greensideupcontracting/

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRNuc7PofUOEHCwMf7NdUzQ/videos?view_as=subscriber

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GreenSideUpContracting/

We would also invite you to come on site during the construction process, so you can see our work in progress!

***

Building is fun, business is great, people are terrific and life is wonderful! 

I ask that you put your trust into Green Side Up Contracting - we not disappoint!!

On your side,

Jay Saveall

www.greensideupcontracting.com

profile:
We are Action Home Services, and we always take action for every construction service that you need. Based in Toronto, Ontario, we are a general contracting company that specializes in a wide range of services. We will help you to design and build an outside living area of your dream. Do not wait! Take action with Action Home Services. Check our website at http://actionhomeservices.ca/ to find out more. 

Our Mission
We aim to become one of the most successful construction companies within Toronto, Ontario. This mission will not happen if our services are not up to the level of what our customers are expecting. Thus our main aim is to provide the best services to our customers. Our level of professionalism will become our barometer for customer satisfaction. We also aim to make it a point to have strong ties with our customers so we can grow the level of our professionalism and gain more trust among our clients.

Our Vision
Our dream is to become the one-stop shop for any kind of construction service that any of our clients need. We initially started with interlocking and asphalt paving, but we are now venturing into other services such as landscaping, pressure washing and sealing, concreting, decks and fences, demolition services and many more. We already have a wide range of service offerings, but we are not satisfied with just these. We are excited about every project that we perform and our possibilities for improvement and additional services are endless.

Our Commitment 
We commit to do whatever it takes to achieve the level of satisfaction our customer deserves. Our workmanship will leave a lasting mark and one that will be a reminder of our professionalism and close ties with our clients. We gained the trust of our customers through hard work that pays off when we see our clients happy with the outcome of our services. We will strive to be cooperative and readily available for any queries or requests our customer needs.

profile:
Beaver Paving Ltd. is a full service asphalt paving and Interlocking company. Established in 1980, Beaver  Paving Ltd. has been operating as family run business for over 35 years. With the original owner who continues to oversee and be involved with all aspects of the business, they have earned a reputation as being an exemplary company who excels in providing quality performance and customer service.
 
OUR GUARANTEE 
Beaver Paving Ltd ,we individually design and engineer your driveway using the highest quality materials combining expertise with experience. Although residential driveways and commercial lot designs and projects may vary from client to client, specifications and skill are always guaranteed to be consistent; from the biggest job to the smallest. 
Beaver Paving provides a full 12 month written guarantee with every contract.
 
Our Services Include: 
*Residential Paving 
*Commercial Paving 
*Asphalt Paving Contracting 
*Driveway Extensions 
*Sub-base Excavation 
*Grading Work, Regrading and Compacting 
*Interlocking Work 
*Concrete Floors and Pads 
*Walkway Reconstruction 
*Parking Lots 
*Industrial Lots 
*Commercial Plazas 
*Condominium Laneways 
*Grinding / Pulverizing 
*Resurfacing 
*Patch Work 
*Asphalt Grindings 
*Catch Basin Installations 
*Painted Line Markings 
*Rural Laneways

profile:
Canada’s Gardenland is a leading domestic landscape construction and maintenance service provider in the Greater Toronto area. Our team of lawn specialists utilizes their knowledge of lawn science and their skills of artistic application to create the perfect look for your specific landscaping scenario. We understand that each property and client taste is different so we work diligently with you and your surroundings to tailor the best approach for meeting those needs. Canada’s Gardenland has both the tools and the experience available to help you bring your landscaping dream to life.
Canada’s Gardenland designs, creates, maintains and provides tools for domestic landscaping projects in the Greater Toronto area. Both artistic landscaping skills and applied lawn science is utilized in order to achieve the perfect atmosphere and our professional team works closely with clients to ensure that projects meet specific needs and requirements.

Proper landscaping requires the application of various aspects in order to make your property look its best. Therefore, Canada’s Gardenland first helps with the design and creation of the right landscaping techniques that complement the natural lay of land as well as any man-made structures on the premises. We also offer a variety of interlocking stone techniques that provide landscaping accents through beautifully designed and applied walkways, driveways and patios.

We can also apply creative outdoor lighting effects so that your landscape is transformed into a stunning sight of beauty after dark and provides safety to those visiting after hours. Quality landscaping maintenance is also offered through sod fertilization, trimming, grooming, replanting and cleaning so that your property always looks its best.

profile:
Pro-Loc Interlocking & Landscape Design is a privately owned company established in 2003. 
With an early focus on residential interlocking and landscaping contracts, Pro-Loc has matured into a full service residential and commercial interlocking company with expertise spanning all aspects of large-scale project disciplines. 
Today, we successfully manage commercial and residential interlocking and landscape design projects all across southern Ontario.

Pro-Loc Interlocking & Landscape Design is a multi-craft employer providing a wide variety of services ranging from individual turnkey installations to large-scale specialty subcontracting assignments including Interlock Paver Installation. 

When schedules matter, we offer a competitive advantage you can count on. We provide outstanding "backstage" support to our field operations helping projects run smoothly. 
In the field, we maintain a steady workforce of skilled craftsmen and project managers allowing projects to progress smoothly to completion.

Our craftsmen take great pride in both the quality of their work and the aesthetic beauty of the finished product. 

We are open for business and we are following all Covid-19 regulations.

Established in l978, Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. has built a reputation for
excellence - specializing in all facets of asphalt paving, concrete work and interlocking
stone.
Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. is a family owned and operated business. Continuing 40 years of experience in the paving business.
Since the beginning, the Company has served Metropolitan of Toronto residents earning respect within the business as one of the most professional and personal companies in the
industry.
With industrial and residential size equipment, no job is to small or big for Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. We use heavy duty equipment for best results.
In April, 2004 Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. was chosen as the business of the week in Toronto.
Customers deal directly with the owners of Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. and each member of the staff has at least l0 years paving experience.
Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. is fully insured and carries a performance bond and is registered with the Ministry of Consumer and Commercial Relations.
Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. is a member of the Better Business Bureau and the Toronto Builders Association.

Our business is built on satisfied customers. All work carries a one year guarantee.

profile: Welcome to Gardenzilla Lawn & Garden. We offer lawn, garden and snow services in Midtown Toronto and East York. We offer exceptional gardening services, with easy online booking and simple pricing. Our most popular services are our garden cleanups and landscape staging, to help homeowners and home sellers restore neglected or overgrown gardens. We also do garden maintenance, garden installation and upgrades, and annual and bulb flower planting.

profile:
Singular Focus:

Most landscape and renovation companies try to serve many types of customers at the same time; homeowners, shopping centers, office buildings, golf courses, and the list goes on. They are pulled in all directions trying to be everything to everyone. At Captain Handy Co, we focus on one customer, you, the homeowner. We have a singular focus on bringing you the best landscaping and interior renovation, the best customer service, and the best value for your home. When you consider that quality renovation can improve the value of your home by 10%-15%, why wouldn’t you hire the one company that focuses specifically on residential landscaping? We are Your Residential Landscape and interior renovation Company.
Easy:

Our business makes your life easier. We are committed to improving the quality of life for our customers so they can spend their time on other things. Our customers are busy and have hectic lives. They do not have time to deal with different companies for lawn care, mowing, design, patio building. Captain Handy Co. offers turn-key solutions to your landscape needs. One call connects you with one of our very qualified Landscape Advisors who will make sure that you are delighted with your landscape. It is that easy.
Hassle-Free:

Ever notice how some companies make it a hassle just to do business with them? Who needs hassles? Life is complicated enough as it is. With Captain Handy Co, you can expect fast response times, clear and concise proposals, and work to be done how and when we promise it would be. You can also expect us to stand behind our work, show up when we say we will and take care of the little things that can take a landscape,renovation and experience, from blah to wow! We take away the hassles so all you have to do is enjoy your landscape.
Professional:

With 5 years under our belts, we know a thing or two about being the professional contractor of choice. Our staff has an average tenure rate of over twelve years, and some team members have been with us for over two decades! They undergo extensive and on-going training to not only assure that your renovation looks fantastic, but also to make sure that you are treated superbly. Our staff members are clearly recognizable in their sharp uniforms so you will know who is on your property. With so many companies claiming to be “professional”, isn’t it nice to work with a company that actually is?
Our Values:

At Captain Handy Co, we provide Tender Loving Care to both you and your interior and landscape renovation. These are our Values:
•	Treat people honestly, fairly and with respect in all situations
•	Create a comfortable environment in which to work and do business
•	Be open to problems and complaints, and work quickly to a fair resolution
•	Present a professional image and working safely
•	Have a “can-do” attitude
•	Stand behind our commitment to quality and service
•	Be active, responsible and positive citizens in the communities in which we work

profile:
We Design, Construct and Maintain outdoor spaces that leave you breathless.

We are Ontario's leading landscaping and construction company, based in Toronto. We pride ourselves in providing professional, accurate and friendly service. We always assure 100% satisfaction to every customer, with quality work that lasts - for years and years of enjoyment.

We will help you with individual design ideas, materials, location recommendations & anything else needed, to get your landscaping project started.

All work is performed in an ethical and patient - yet timely - manner. And the quality is proudly guaranteed for up to 5 years.

profile:
Mr. Interlock Landscape & Construction is a professional residential and commercial design and build firm servicing the York Region and Greater Toronto Area communities.
 
With over 30 years of experience in interlocking and paving installations, we help our clients create a distinctive design element that will magnify their homes allure, increase its value while offering a unique look customized to meet their landscape desires.
 
We take pride in providing our clients with original and timeless designs, innovative ideas, quality construction, prompt and professional service, outstanding warranty and seamless flow of project implementation from start to finish.
 
Our construction expertise spans across a variety of materials from natural stone, flagstone, marble to cobblestones, standard pavers, concrete and asphalt.
 
We also specialize in a variety of project types such as driveways, patios, stairs, retaining walls, swimming pools, outdoor kitchenettes, outdoor living spaces, outdoor lighting, outdoor audio and more.
 
Our mission is to enhance and beautify the communities we enter by supplying our clients with a uniquely designed landscape project that adheres to our motto "Do It Once, Do It Right". All while providing our clients with unparalleled service through our consultation, planning and execution resulting in long lasting relationships and an abundance of word of mouth referrals.

Our Guarantee
We Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. construct each project using the highest quality materials, while providing the highest level of expertise and customer service. profile:
About Us

We are a family-run business serving Toronto, GTA and the surrounding areas for over 10 years. During our time in business we have served hundreds of happy customers by staying true to our company values. We do all kinds of outdoor stonework, including interlock sealing, interlock repairs and installation, fixing and installing steps, curbs, flower beds, retaining walls. 

Our values

Exceptional Workmanship

We invest a lot into hiring, training and retaining good workers. Our workers are knowledgeable, courteous and have exceptional attention to detail. From job preparation to clean-up, we will work hard to perform above and beyond your expectations. 

Highest quality supplies and equipment

We use only industrial-grade supplies and equipment. All our suppliers are local, reputable manufacturers. Equipment we use is the best available, allowing us to deliver a service that is both of high quality and efficient. 

Client satisfaction

We would leave no stone unturned (figurately and in some cases literally) until you are satisfied with our work. We will work hard to gain your repeat business and referrals. 

Personalized Service and Quotes

No job is the same. This is why we take the time to assess the job that has to be done before presenting you with a proposal. Then we meticulously follow what we promised.

Reliable communication

You will have a manager in charge of your project who will always be there to answer your questions and to keep you posted on the progress.

profile:
Sunken Interlock?  Call Leveled Ground Inc.
 
We're the Interlock repair specialists.  This is all we do everyday all day. We are experts at fixing interlocking driveways, walkways, patios, stairs and retaining walls and routinely fix:
 
•	Tire marks and depressions from your car.
•	Where the driveway meets the garage, sidewalk or curb.
•	Where water is moving towards the house.
•	After waterproofing or other pipe work has been done.
•	Sloping or collapsing stairs. 
•	Essential repair work before listing a house for resale.
•	Small extensions to driveways to allow for an extra car or give more room in the winter with the snow.
_____________________________________________________
This kind of work is all we do, we're really good at it, enjoy doing it, and take pride at being really good at it and leaving with happy customers (who routinely call us back for other work in the future).
 
•	We arrive when we say we will, call if we're running late, do the work properly the first time, have all our workers on each job so it gets done as quickly and efficiently as possible, and leave your property clean and looking good as new.  If there are any issues that need attention, we'll take care of it immediately so you aren't left waiting for us to come back.  

•	Above all we want satisfied customers who feel good through the entire process about hiring us to fix their interlock. 
_____________________________________________________
We service Midtown Toronto from Sheppard down to Bloor, and from The DVP to the Allen Expressway. We're not able to work outside of this area due to traffic and logistics.  
 
Call to arrange a free estimate with Adam Sidenberg (The owner) who  will come meet you in person, see what problems need fixing, and discuss the options for how we can fix it.

profile:
Landscaping Contractors & Designers, Interlocking Stone.

OWNERSHIP AND CREDENTIALS
Hofstetter Landscaping is owned and operated by Rick and Ashleigh Hofstetter. Our “baby” was born in 1989 and is now 23 years old. (In case you’re wondering how old we are...suffices to say we are evergreens. :-)  Did we tell you we are a landscaping company?) 
From the beginning, we have always endeavoured to do the best quality work possible for our clients. We specialize in landscaping and that’s one of the reasons our “baby” has no siblings—no sister companies, no associates, no partners, no branches. Landscaping is what we do and we do it really well.

A TORONTO LANDSCAPING COMPANY WITH A DIFFERENCE
Ever since we started, and even more so now, we find the market exploding with Toronto landscaping companies that make a big noise about “cheap, cheap”. Now, if they were selling birds, it would be okay, but they are not, right? And yet, we often lose a job to a cheap company that “specializes” in being a “Jack-of-all-trades”. Do we want to compete with them? No. But does that mean we are frightfully expensive? Not at all! In fact, our goal is always to ensure that our customers get the best value for money and a landscape that makes them the envy of the neighbourhood without breaking the bank.

As we come across customers who do their due diligence by comparing quotes, we are very mindful and respectful of the fact that one needs to be price conscious. It’s when we are told about a competitive quote that implies “the other guy” can get the job done for less than it costs us to buy quality materials, the alarm bells go off. He needs a hefty deposit from you to pay his guys for the last job done, and of course, there is always that famous curbside taillight guarantee!

We would like to go on and tell you what we have learned and found out in these past 23 years but you wouldn't be able to read it all...

WHY YOU SHOULD CHOOSE TO ENGAGE OUR LANDSCAPING SERVICES IN TORONTO 

All we want to say is this—we do top quality work with a guarantee you can count on, every single time. If it’s not to your liking we'll do what it takes to make it right. We'll be there in years to come, particularly if the weather has given the work a beating. 

•	We are fully covered with 5 million liability insurance and WSIB approved. 
•	Our crew is safety certified or they don't work for us. 
•	Our business has City of Toronto licensing.
•	Each team member has government ID.
•	We pay our taxes and are an ethical, honest, law-abiding enterprise.

Yes, you will find cheaper Toronto landscaping companies out there. Will you find one better than us in terms of reputation for quality work and customer references? Not likely. 

Please visit our website (www.HofstetterLandscaping.com) or call us today at 647-955-8382 to book a free, no obligation landscaping consultation in Toronto.

profile:
Bestloc Interlocking is trusted and respected landscape design and Installation company operating in the Greater Toronto and Surrounding Areas. As a proud and certified member of ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), we provide our clients with award winning landscape designs and industry leading installations. Bestloc was found on two main principles of encouraging family outdoor living and building structures that last.

Many years ago, Ryan Morant, founder and president started out being a labourer, where he developed his passion for the trade. He then became a foreman, and inspector, and subsequently a teacher. Under his leadership, our professional team of highly skilled and qualified personnel provides innovative landscape designs. With over 15 years of planting and masonry experience, and hundreds of thousands of square feet laid, Bestloc Interlocking embodies the values of strength, performance, and passion. We are dedicated to providing our clients with custom landscaping solutions.

We are in constant communication with our friends at ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), and are always up-to-date on industry leading techniques on landscape designs and installations. We offer good communication with our clients from the beginning of each project to its completion. Our experienced project management means your project is completed on time and on budget.

Furthermore, we complete every task with a commitment to integrity and a devotion to excellence using the best quality products guaranteed to leave a lasting impression. If you wish to create the finest outdoor living experience for you and your family, please do not hesitate to contact Bestloc Interlocking for a free consultation/estimate.
warranty_terms: 2 Years Warranty. Kindly Request Further Information

profile:
We started our Landscape and Interlocking Stone business in 1994 based on three pillars:  Integrity, Quality, and Service.

ONE job at a time… Unlike many other businesses we do ONE job at a time. It is important to us to be able to focus all our efforts into each customer so that they get the best in personal attention and their project is completed as expected and on time.

No Sub-Contracted Work…   We do all the work ourselves. Our employees are highly qualified, talented, and honest. We wouldn’t trust your project and our reputation to anyone else.

We deliver what we promise to do. We carry out our work according to what our customers want and expect. We strive to deliver the best results at the least possible cost for the client.
Our work exceeds construction standards and client’s expectations. We take satisfaction in showing our customers how their project is been done so that they may appreciate the workmanship that goes into their project.

As a Landscape Contractor and Designer....
Our Goal… To exceed the expectations of every client by doing our work with Honesty, Quality, and Professionalism.                                  
Our approach… We first listen to what our clients want and make suggestions based on that and our experience. We then proceed to work in an efficient and flexible manner through every phase of the project to suit the client's needs.
 
We are happy to provide you with the following services and more:
Patios, walkways, steps, porches, verandas, pergolas, driveways, flower beds, gardens, planting, sprinklers, lighting, stone BBQs, stone fireplaces, and much more.

Letter from Danilo Otero, owner of Royal Town Landscape Development, March 2012:

Dear Customers,

I would like to thank you and congratulate you for helping children in Nicaragua go to school. Because of you, we were able to provide school supplies to 100 kids this past month and we are already working to provide another one hundred sets of school supplies this Summer. 

Thank You!  You made a big difference.

Regards,

Danilo

profile:
Our mission is to enhance lifestyles by providing aesthetically appealing home and property improvements with professional care and quality. Hardscape Interlock Design thrives to being nationally recognized as revolutionizing the paving and outdoor lifestyle industry by becoming the preferred choice. We are deeply committed to maintaining the industry’s highest standards of customer service and support. We listen to our customer needs and strive everyday to earn the credibility that has been associated with our company name and operations since we began.
Whether you’re looking for high-quality, durable driveways or planning to design an outdoor retreat with interlocking paving stones, choose Hardscapes Specialists to do the job. While being recognized for our high quality of work, Hardscapes is committed to providing you with great customer service. Our experts look to cut no corners and are determined to not only meet, but exceed your all expectations. With our dynamic designs and superior customer service, we are certain that you’ll be ecstatic with the outcome of the project

Having a hard time constructing a unique design for your home? Not a problem- Hardscapes Sales representatives have between 5-10 years of skilled and creative installation experience in the industry. They are also trained to help you construct exceptional quality and aesthetically beautiful designs to meet all your outdoor desires. If your still having trouble envisioning the outcome of your project, Hardscapes also offers a rendered design of your home to help you reach beyond your imagination and help visualize the final product. At Hardscapes, we have the experience and the knowledge to take your vision and make it into a reality. We plan on making your home the talk of the neighbourhood!
Hardscapes takes pride on our quality of work, while also being respectful to your neighbours by maintaining a clean and hazard free environment for the duration of the job. We guarantee that you will work with the same employees to oversee your project from concepts to its completion. Our paving stone installers are professional, respectful, fast and reliable. While many of our competitors leave projects incomplete and return to them at a later date, we are committed to concentrating on your job from start to finish, before moving onto another project. We are a design company full of innovative ideas and dedicated staff.

Why Choose Bancheri Bros. as your interlocking installer?

Bancheri Bros. Interlocking and Paving Corp is a family owned and operated busines, this means that at all times there is an owner supervising the site. This helps ensure sure the quality and workmanship of all our projects are beyond the customers expectations.

For over 20 years Bancheri Bros. has always been about customers first. We have all of the latest tools and equipment to accommodate any size job, we can offer products from any of the top industry suppliers and we start and finish each job on time and efficiently.
products: Interlocking concrete pavers are a smart and elegant design choice. They are manufactured to withstand weight and weather. They are laid in bedding sand just as flagstone, cobblestone, and brick, but they interlock to provide a perfect, stable fit. They come in a wide variety of colors, shapes, textures, and designs. Interlocking pavers are easy to maintain and they provide an excellent drainage system for your driveway.

profile:
A&K Group Contracting

as our name implies is an alliance of professional skilled individuals serving the Greater Toronto area. With over 2 decades of experience ranging from exterior landscaping to indoor renovations. We are committed to providing all our clients with the highest standard of quality and integrity, for this is the very reason why we’ve created a standard unparalleled that others only hope to achieve.  

Why us?

Quality

100% satisfaction. Whether it be from basic initial designs to final steps of installation we have proven time and time again that we are your #1 choice.  

Delivering quality work is our top priority. We hope to build long lasting relationships with all our clients. 

Experience

With over hundreds of projects completed in our name, there isn’t a job we haven't done or a problem we’ve never seen. We specialize in functional, conceptual designs that serve both form and function while maximizing client's investment return. 

Achievement

With our vast wealth of knowledge and hands on experience, our clients can reassured that every effort is made to efficiently incorporate all cost saving initiatives to deliver outstanding projects at competitive rates without compromising quality. 

So if you’re in the market for a quick quote or in need of bespoke services tailored to your budget. Our professional staff are readily available to serve you, allow us the opportunity to work together so we can exceed all your expectations. We are just a phone call away!

profile:
With decades of experience in the industry, our experts at Tikal Paving LTD have a reputation for designing and building beautiful, durable projects. We are your one-stop-shop for a variety of outdoor installation and repair services whether your needs are residential, commercial, industrial, or municipal.

Each project is carefully engineered to suit your individual needs and executed by our skilled and licensed contractors. Our team takes attention to detail seriously and uses top-quality materials for finished products that are as durable as they are visually appealing. That’s why any project completed by Tikal Paving LTD is guaranteed for one year. Our range of services includes landscaping, asphalt, concrete, interlocking brick, and snow plowing.

Our approach to outdoor projects is in our name; Tikal Paving. Tikal National Park is a 576 km² area in Guatemala that perfectly combines natural wonders with architectural feats that have survived enduring the elements for centuries. We believe the harmony between stunning natural landscaping and durable architectural elements is not only achievable, but a requirement for a functional and enjoyable space.

Not only do we guarantee superior workmanship, but we are also dedicated to providing the best customer service in the area. Get in touch with us to discuss your project and we will be happy to answer all your questions and provide a free quote.

profile:
Paving, Interlocking, Concrete
M.n.B. Paving Ltd. offers a full range of hardscaping services including interlocking, steps and walls, pool decks and surrounds, asphalt and concrete.

Commercial
We understand that you want to work with a company that cares as much about your property as you do. Here’s why you should consider M.n.B. as your partner:

Experienced

We have over 27 years of experience, helping homeowners and businesses create the landscape of their dreams. We’ve created the perfect design in all types of conditions and have the happy customers to prove it.

Our team is experienced in all aspects of landscape design and build projects, including interlocking stone, retaining walls, asphalt and concrete work, and putting the finishing touches on pools.

Professional

Using the best products on the market, backed by the latest technology and machines, our team is meticulous about your project. We prepare your site, carefully perform the installation, and always clean up after ourselves. Our workers conduct themselves with the utmost professionalism, because we know we’re working where you live.

Quality, built to last

We’re committed to creating the environment you’ve been dreaming about, one that will improve your curb appeal, and leave a lasting impression. Each project is closely monitored for quality, and the company owner is involved in your project from start to finish to ensure your satisfaction.

M.n.B. Paving is a member of the Better Business Bureau with an A+ rating.
services:
Our goal is to create a beautiful and functional landscape, whatever your need.

We work with you to determine traffic patterns, living spaces, and focal areas of your landscape. We begin your project with a properly prepared base that’s compacted, leveled and graded; then proceed to build the landscape according to your approved design.

At Green Scene Landscaping, we strive to be a single source for complete landscaping and hardscaping services, from outdoor kitchens to swimming pool installation, interlocking patio design and everything between.

Avoid the hassle of working with multiple contractors and build a relationship with the team that can service your entire property from start to finish.

Our experienced landscaping contractors are available throughout your landscape design, product and material selection, all the way to project completion (and even beyond).

Green Scene Landscaping uses only the highest quality materials in the industry, so you get the highest quality, longest-lasting work.
--

--
And since we are industry certified, members of Landscape Ontario, and keep our crews informed and educated with industry trends, you can always expect the very best.

profile:
WELCOME TO DON VALLEY STONE​​

Don Valley Stone is one of the most experienced and respected construction company in Toronto, Canada.  For over a decade, we have been transforming the ideas and visions of our clients into award-winning projects. 

We build with the intention of exceeding our clients expectations for quality, safety, functionality, and aesthetics, and deliver finished products that stand the test of time.

Don Valley Stone has been helping our clients build for over a decade. Canadian owned and operated since 2005, we have grown from a small local excavating into one of the most capable and trusted general construction company.

There is no project too small or too big, Don Valley Stone is capable of taking projects of all sizes and levels. 
From simple window installation to some of the most complex electrical engineering; we can build it all and we do. 

Don Valley Stone's breadth of capabilities ensures that we are able to meet our clients needs every time, on every front. But, what truly sets us apart from our competition is our people.  Their dedication to providing world-class service to our clients, resolve for delivering exceptional work, capacity for innovation and problem solving.

profile:
LEADERS IN RESIDENTIAL INTERLOCKING

1. What kind of services do you provide?
We provide many different services at Apex, such as; interlocking (new and repair), flagstone installation, natural stone installation and landscape design.

2. Do we need to stay home during the process?
It is not necessary to remain at home during the process. We sign a contract beforehand so both party's are clear on the job, therefore we strive to complete the job with as little upheaval as possible.

3. How long have you been in business?
We are a family run business that has run for 25 years.

4. Am I as the customer responsible for the disposal of materials?
No you are not. Apex will take care of all removal of materials at the end of your job and we ensure to leave your job site clean and tidy.

5. Are we able to view actual stone samples before starting the job?
        Yes, we can show our customers a variety of stones and colours to ensure                   your satisfaction with the job.
